Terms of Service (ToS) for SmartClock
Effective Date: 4/27/2025
Owner: Pixelnauts
Contact: pixelcryptonauts@gmail.com

Pixelnauts ("we", "us", "our") is committed to protecting your privacy. This mobile application ("SmartClock") does not collect or store any personal data.

Local Storage:
User-entered reminders and notes are stored locally on the user's device only. We do not access, collect, or share this information.

External Links:
The SmartClock app may open an external website. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of third-party websites.

No Tracking:
We do not collect location data, analytics data, or any other personal information.

No Payments:
The SmartClock app does not process payments. If users choose to donate, they are redirected to external platforms.

Children's Privacy:
The SmartClock app is intended for general audiences and does not knowingly collect personal data from children under 13.

Changes:
We may update this Privacy Policy. Any changes will be posted here.

For questions, please contact us at pixelcryptonauts@gmail.com.
